{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/git-command-list-post","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"9ece261b-ddcd-5afb-81d4-3f6ede1919f9","html":"<!-- ![test8](/media/image-3.jpg) -->\n<h2 id=\"git-작업의-흐름\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#git-%EC%9E%91%EC%97%85%EC%9D%98-%ED%9D%90%EB%A6%84\" aria-label=\"git 작업의 흐름 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Git 작업의 흐름</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c4bd1c045ad8da3d4d599f3df2bba05b/6af66/gitflow.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.5625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/c4bd1c045ad8da3d4d599f3df2bba05b/8ac56/gitflow.webp 240w,\n/static/c4bd1c045ad8da3d4d599f3df2bba05b/d3be9/gitflow.webp 480w,\n/static/c4bd1c045ad8da3d4d599f3df2bba05b/0ba47/gitflow.webp 640w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/c4bd1c045ad8da3d4d599f3df2bba05b/8ff5a/gitflow.png 240w,\n/static/c4bd1c045ad8da3d4d599f3df2bba05b/e85cb/gitflow.png 480w,\n/static/c4bd1c045ad8da3d4d599f3df2bba05b/6af66/gitflow.png 640w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/c4bd1c045ad8da3d4d599f3df2bba05b/6af66/gitflow.png\"\n          alt=\"gitflow\"\n          title=\"gitflow\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\nWorking directory는 실제 파일\nIndex는 staging area\nHEAD는 최종 commit 확정본을 나타낸다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"git-init\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#git-init\" aria-label=\"git init permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>git init</h2>\n<p><strong>.git</strong> 이라는 하위 디렉토리를 만든다. 새로운 git 저장소가 만들어지는 것이다.\n<strong>.git</strong> 디렉토리에는 저장소에 필요한 뼈대 파일(Skeleton)이 들어있고 이 명령만으로는 프로젝트의 어떤 파일도 관리하지 않는다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"git-add-파일-이름\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#git-add-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EC%9D%B4%EB%A6%84\" aria-label=\"git add 파일 이름 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>git add &#x3C;파일 이름></h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">git add .</code></pre></div>\n<p>git이 파일을 관리하게 만드려면 저장소에 파일을 추가하고 커밋해야 한다. <strong>git add</strong> 명령으로 변경된 파일을 인덱스에 추가한다.\ngit의 기본 작업 흐름에서 첫단계이다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"git-commit--m-이번-확정본에-대한-설명\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#git-commit--m-%EC%9D%B4%EB%B2%88-%ED%99%95%EC%A0%95%EB%B3%B8%EC%97%90-%EB%8C%80%ED%95%9C-%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85\" aria-label=\"git commit  m 이번 확정본에 대한 설명 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>git commit -m “이번 확정본에 대한 설명”</h2>\n<p>실제 변경 내용을 확정하기 위한 명령어다. 변경된 파일이 HEAD에 반영된다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"git-push-origin-master\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#git-push-origin-master\" aria-label=\"git push origin master permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>git push origin master</h2>\n<p>로컬저장소의 HEAD 안에 머물고 있는 변경 내용을 원격 서버로 올린다. 다른 branch를 발행하려면 master를 원하는 branch 이름으로 바꿔 준다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"git-remote\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#git-remote\" aria-label=\"git remote permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>git remote</h2>\n<p>현재 프로젝트에 등록된 리모트 저장소를 확인할 수 있다. 이 명령은 리모트 저장소의 단축 이름을 보여준다.\n저장소를 Clone하면 <strong>origin</strong> 이라는 리모트 저장소가 자동으로 등록되기 때문에 ‘origin’이라는 이름을 볼 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ git remote\norigin</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>-v</strong> 옵션을 주면 단축이름과 URL을 함께 볼 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ git remote -v\norigin\thttps://github.com/DanSJKim/DanSJKim.github.io.git (fetch)\norigin\thttps://github.com/DanSJKim/DanSJKim.github.io.git (push)</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"git-remote-add-단축이름-url\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#git-remote-add-%EB%8B%A8%EC%B6%95%EC%9D%B4%EB%A6%84-url\" aria-label=\"git remote add 단축이름 url permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>git remote add &#x3C;단축이름> <url></h2>\n<p>기존에 있던 원격 저장소를 복제한 것이 아니라면 원격 서버의 주소를 git에게 알려줘야 한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ git remote add origin &lt;원격 서버 주소&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 492px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3951d31d867dd62b40ccb086df3e0c97/5c6e9/branch.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 33.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/3951d31d867dd62b40ccb086df3e0c97/8ac56/branch.webp 240w,\n/static/3951d31d867dd62b40ccb086df3e0c97/d3be9/branch.webp 480w,\n/static/3951d31d867dd62b40ccb086df3e0c97/9d6da/branch.webp 492w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 492px) 100vw, 492px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/3951d31d867dd62b40ccb086df3e0c97/8ff5a/branch.png 240w,\n/static/3951d31d867dd62b40ccb086df3e0c97/e85cb/branch.png 480w,\n/static/3951d31d867dd62b40ccb086df3e0c97/5c6e9/branch.png 492w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 492px) 100vw, 492px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/3951d31d867dd62b40ccb086df3e0c97/5c6e9/branch.png\"\n          alt=\"branch\"\n          title=\"branch\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"git-branch-branchname\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#git-branch-branchname\" aria-label=\"git branch branchname permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>git branch <branchname></h2>\n<p>현재 브랜치에서 새로운 브랜치를 생성한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ git branch Feature-1</code></pre></div>\n<p>옵션을 지정하지 않고 branch 명령어를 실행하면 브랜치 목록 전체를 확인할 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ git branch\n  Feature-1\n* master\n// 앞부분에 * 이 붙어있는 것이 선택 된 브랜치다.</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"git-checkout-branchname\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#git-checkout-branchname\" aria-label=\"git checkout branchname permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>git checkout <branchname></h2>\n<p>앞서 만든 <strong>Feature-1</strong>라는 브랜치를 사용하기 위해 이 브랜치를 사용하겠다고 명시적으로 지정해 준다.\n<strong>checkout</strong>이란 내가 사용할 브랜치를 지정하는 것을 의미한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ git checkout Feature-1\nSwitched to branch &#39;Feature-1&#39;</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"git-clone\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#git-clone\" aria-label=\"git clone permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>git clone</h2>\n<p>다른 프로젝트에 참여하거나 Git 저장소를 복사하고싶을 때 <strong>git clone</strong>을 사용한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ git clone https://github.com/DanSJKim/DanSJKim.github.io.git</code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/git-command-list-post","tagSlugs":null},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-02-06T22:40:32.169Z","description":"Git의 주요 명령어를 정리해 보았다.","tags":null,"title":"Git 명령어 정리","socialImage":"/media/image-3.jpg"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/git-command-list-post"}}}